Sentencas: The single cell with the Nio.gFeo.2+SDC anode exhibited a maximum power density of 1.43 W cm(-2) at 800 degrees C and 0.62 W cm(-2) at 700 degrees C.

Sentencas: A stable performance with essentially negligible increase in anode overpotential was observed during about 160 h operation of the cell with the Ni0.8Fe0.2 + SDC anode at 800 degrees C with a fixed current density of 1875 mA cm(-2).
